Véronique Vendell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/V%C3%A9ronique_Vendell 0 Véronique Vendell (born Véronique Duraffourd, 21 July 1942) is a French actress. She appeared mainly in French and German productions, but had roles in both Peter Glenville's Becket and Sam Peckinpah's Cross of Iron and its sequel Breakthrough.
